hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: No, I'm not particularly sporty buy psychoactive drugs online Grain Store gives off a straight forward visual message: bright, light and clean, ceilings busy with fashionable lighting, walls busy with utensils. Its menu is full of idiosyncrasy: dishes are matched with cocktails; meat is downgraded from the centrepiece to the periphery; the waiting staff are instructed to call it the “corn and quinoa tamale” rather than the pork belly. Of the starters, I could find only two of 10 that you might conceivably find on any other menu. That’s not necessarily a compliment; having tasted the innovation, I’d say the line between originality and misguidedness was crossed more than once.
